    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "BOISE, April 30.-Accompanied\nby her daughters and a nurse Mrs,\nWilliam d. Haywood arrived here\nyesterday from Denver to be near\nher husband in his trial which be-\ngins May T. They were permitted\na happy visit with the imprisoned\nminer yesterday and will be allow\ned to see him frequently. Mrs.\nHaywood is aninvalid.\n\n\nDenial of any intention to ask\nfor further change of venue was\nmade yesterday by E. p. Richard\nson, chief counsel for the defense."
    }
  ]
